The paper could also be categorized under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) as it involves the use of machine learning techniques to generate images.

Graphics (cs.GR) is another possible category as the paper deals with image synthesis and style transfer which are important topics in computer graphics. 

Finally, Multimedia (cs.MM) is another possible category as the paper deals with image synthesis which is a common task in multimedia applications.
